        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="rUX7LjXCXM_KjE6oEwl8-16" value="&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 11px;&quot;&gt;It monitors the bitcoin network for IPC-related transactions, such as &lt;i&gt;createChild()&lt;/i&gt;, &lt;i&gt;joinSubnet()&lt;/i&gt;, &lt;i&gt;deposit()&lt;/i&gt;, and &lt;i&gt;propagate().&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/font&gt;" style="shape=note;strokeWidth=2;fontSize=14;size=20;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#fff2cc;strokeColor=#d6b656;fontColor=#666600;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="900" y="806" width="220" height="60" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="rUX7LjXCXM_KjE6oEwl8-17" value="&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11px;&quot;&gt;We run a bitcoin full node, connected to a local testnet. It is also possible to use a trusted full node.&lt;/span&gt;" style="shape=note;strokeWidth=2;fontSize=14;size=20;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#fff2cc;strokeColor=#d6b656;fontColor=#666600;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="900" y="956" width="220" height="54" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="rUX7LjXCXM_KjE6oEwl8-18" value="&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 11px;&quot;&gt;It creates the required bitcoin transactions (e.g, to implement the &lt;i&gt;createChild()&lt;/i&gt; and &lt;i&gt;joinSubnet()&lt;/i&gt; functionalities) and submits them over PRC to the local bitcoin node.&lt;/font&gt;" style="shape=note;strokeWidth=2;fontSize=14;size=20;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#fff2cc;strokeColor=#d6b656;fontColor=#666600;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="900" y="876" width="220" height="70" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="rUX7LjXCXM_KjE6oEwl8-19" value="&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11px;&quot;&gt;It keeps track of IPC-related state on bitcoin, such as existing subnets and their parameteers, and exposes an interface for modiying it (e.g., create new subnet, join an existing).&lt;/span&gt;" style="shape=note;strokeWidth=2;fontSize=14;size=20;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#fff2cc;strokeColor=#d6b656;fontColor=#666600;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="900" y="710" width="220" height="85" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
